# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore everything by default and re-include only needed files.
# NOTE: the build context is the repo root (operator/, csi-driver/ and atlas-lib/ are
# nested), so re-include patterns must be depth-agnostic (**/) — a bare "go.mod" would
# only match a root-level file and would exclude operator/go.mod, csi-driver/go.mod, etc.
**

# Re-include Go source files (but not *_test.go)
!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

# Re-include Go module files
!**/go.mod
!**/go.sum

# Re-include bundle directory
!**/bundle/

# Re-include LICENSE file
!LICENSE